_sText:
Mw2_HighRise_ly

This map was made by lucky for css. I love the HighRise map on Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2. So i figured the people who don't have mw2 or just love the map. Would love to play it on css.


The Map Took me a lot of time to make it look nice and try to make it as much as the original one. Some things i changed about the map and something are the same.


//// Small list of Things you can still do ////

* Walk and Camp on the crane 
* Aim under the hele platform 
* Get on top of the Smaller Building 
* Get on top of the shop sign 
* And More.....


Its not 100% like the original But i think it looks nice and the game play is real cool. 


The Map is not 100% finished this is the first beta if u see errors or see something u want change just comment and let me know :)


Thanks!! Rate And Comment!
